data.description: Fantastic 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom condo for sale in a great location!  This spacious condo features a separate dining room, one large bedroom with a large closet and doors to your own private balcony!  Also featured is a large bathroom, a private laundry room with tons of space for storage etc, balcony off of the living room and a cozy fireplace.  All Appliances are included and the unit comes with a carport parking space.  Another bonus is the condo is located just .29 miles to the nearest light rail station, get anywhere in the city without having to drive!  Amenities of Cherry Grove East condos include a pool and tennis courts for your summer enjoyment!
